<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Users and User groups are special types of Content. This means you creat=
e and edit them in the same way as you manage all other Content in your sys=
tem.</p>
<p>However, you cannot access Users and User groups from the normal Content=
 tree. Instead, you have to use the Admin Panel.</p>=20
